   </iframe>
  </p>
  <font face="Arial">
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
   </p>
   <hr align="left" color="#000000" size="1"/>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    <br/>
    Sample sentence:
	Do you like to build a snowmen? = YOU LIKE MAKE SNOW-MAN?
   </p>
   <p style="margin-top: 0; margin-bottom: 0">
    <br/>
    <iframe allow="accelerometer; autoplay; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/0ld4vhLaLZk?rel=0" width="560">
